{"title":"居庸关","authors":["张成良"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"居庸关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张成良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反反复复地修关设隘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次比一次坚固、险要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但一次次被攻破"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守关者被攻关者所破"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破关者又让给新的攻关者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴与亡在这里重复着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个王朝一个王朝在这里重复着……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今我从这里经过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那已修复的关隘垛口上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛看到一个个朝代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同在那关门上曾挂过的走马灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽闪忽闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽明忽灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史如烟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过多的仇杀与遗恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已于洞开的关口流去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而一轮崛起的火红的中华民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的朝阳高悬……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}